{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations/task-92","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada neko kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">as much as</span>, govori o tome da se nešto radi u najvećoj mogućoj meri. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">if you eat as much cake as you can</span>, znači da jedete toliko kolača koliko možete, dok više ne možete da jedete.</p>\n<p>Poslušaj zvuk i odgovori na pitanje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations/task-92"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Brian anataka nini?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Kuendelea kuwa na motisha nyingi</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kupata motisha kidogo kidogo kwa muda</p>","feedback":"<p>Brajan želi da uzbuđenje ostane veliko, a ne da opadne.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kuwa na motisha tu kwa changamoto rahisi</p>","feedback":"<p>Brian anapenda kutatua changamoto, si rahisi tu.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kutafuta motisha nje ya kazi</p>","feedback":"<p>Brajan govori o uzbuđenju zbog rešavanja izazova, a ne o tome gde pronaći motivaciju.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Brian","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.1-3.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":49.3,"finishTimestamp":55.76},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background